    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/b9a85aa31ba9fd6c03c1314e63ebfdd7.avif?t=1758817325\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><br>In this game, you will have the chance to fulfill a dream many share — getting sex for free! But it won’t be as easy as it sounds. You’ll need wit, cunning, and charm, and sometimes, you may even have to put in some effort to achieve your goal while avoiding spending your hard-earned shekels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique heroines.</strong> Try to impress the playful Vika, win over the mysterious Alina, and avoid embarrassing yourself in front of the statuesque Olga Ivanovna.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/708ee3fe02ef12d8ce87522e79e9e2c6.poster.avif?t=1758817325\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/708ee3fe02ef12d8ce87522e79e9e2c6.webm?t=1758817325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/708ee3fe02ef12d8ce87522e79e9e2c6.mp4?t=1758817325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse locations.</strong> You have plenty of options — the Museum, the Restaurant, and even the heroines’ Homes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/1c7930e3d4ececa20d426f1f307047f1.poster.avif?t=1758817325\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/1c7930e3d4ececa20d426f1f307047f1.webm?t=1758817325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/1c7930e3d4ececa20d426f1f307047f1.mp4?t=1758817325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exciting dates.</strong> Experiment with different approaches: prepare in advance or go with the flow, create spontaneous adventures, engage in philosophical conversations, or simply enjoy the moment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/6a0a0c817378173ca10594fad2c40ecb.poster.avif?t=1758817325\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/6a0a0c817378173ca10594fad2c40ecb.webm?t=1758817325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055230/extras/6a0a0c817378173ca10594fad2c40ecb.mp4?t=1758817325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
